I'm looking for anyone whose willing to trade some 1914 Crack Jack
cards graded PSA 1 or 2 or equivalent, in exchange for some graded 
T206 cards, grades 2 thru 5. I've got some HOF'ers, rare backs and 
the like. Please e-mail me at [url]star6240@att.net[/url] with a list of cards you 
have available to trade. The T206 cards are strictly for trade and not 
for sale.

Thanks,

ErikV
